Ahh, indeed, I missed that and focused on the additionalProperties.
Instead use unevaluatedProperties: false and drop all properties already
in dsi-controller.yaml.

> 
>>> +properties:
>>> +  compatible:
>>> +    items:
>>> +      - enum:
>>> +          - apple,j293-summit
